      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "URANA PARALLAX (1) was a sharp 34.51 winner of a Grade 4/5 at this track last start. Can measure up again if runs up to latest time. JONI BLACK (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from seven tries. Was out of the placings last time (38.05) at Bendigo in a Special conditions H, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. SHIMA BLUSH (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (35.25) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Worth another chance. REGGAE GIRL (6) jumps at a shorter trip and still warrants respect.",
